h3 Sizes
p.-text
  | Apply size classes to render pickers larger or smaller: <code>-sm</code>, <code>-md</code>, <code>-lg</code>.
  | The default size is <code>-md</code>.
ul#a-tabs--Sizes.a-tabs
  li.-active
    a(href="#Sm") Size -sm
  li
    a(href="#Md") Size -md
  li
    a(href="#Lg") Size -lg

.example.-mb--3
  #Sm.a-tabs-panel.-active
    .-p--4
      each type in ['Radio1 -sm','Radio2 -sm']
        .m-picker.-sm
          input(type="radio", class="a-picker", name='box', id=`ri-${type}`)
          label(for=`ri-${type}`)
            .m-picker__content--start
